                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-293-victim2382 t18320705-293-viclabel1537"></join>s. On the 23rd of June a coat was stolen from their door - I had seen it at half-past ten o'clock, and missed it about eleven; I saw it brought in by the officer, between seven and eight, the same evening.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320705-293-person2385">
                  WILLIAM 
                  LAW
               <interp inst="t18320705-293-person2385" type="surname" value="LAW"></interp>
